<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
VI. Collection of Information 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Regulations at &sect;441.152 contain collection of information requirements that are subject to the Paperwork
